                </div>
                <div class="Section">
                    <p>
                        <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                            <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">助記詞用於恢復錢包資產，擁有助記詞即可完全控制錢包資產，丟失助記詞即丟失錢包資產</font>
                        </font>
                        <a>
                            <font style="vertical-align: inherit;"></font>
                        </a>
                        <font style="vertical-align: inherit;"></font>
                    </p>
                    <div class="Note Note--warning">
                        <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                            <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">請務必牢記助記詞並妥善保存，CryptoDogs不存儲用護助記詞，無法提供找回功能</font>
                        </font>
                    </div>
                    <a class="Button Button--love Button--larger nextStep">
                        <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                            <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">下壹步</font>
                        </font>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="Hero transaction-password">
        <div class="Container Container--sm Container--center">
            <h2 class="Hero-h2">
                <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                    <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                        填寫交易密碼
                    </font>
                </font>
            </h2>
            <form>
                <div class="Section">
                    <img class="ProfileHeader-image ProfileHeader-image --clickable" src="../images/icons/head.svg">
                </div>

                <div class="Section auxiliaryWordSection">
                    <div class="InputButtons-group">
                        <label for="address">
                            <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                                <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">確認助記詞</font>
                            </font>
                        </label>
                        <textarea class="InputButtons InputButtons--readonly InputButtons-input auxiliaryWordConfirm" placeholder="請按序選擇剛剛生成的助記詞" maxlength="100"></textarea>
